snippet.title: Leaves Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Leaves is  is a contemplative, episodic game on a missing girl.
Get ready to experience a branching, immersive story.
Branch 1 is the first episode launching on Steam by Q3 2020.

WISHLIST: bit.ly/wishlist-Leaves 

Coming for PC Windows and Steam VR.

Music by John Kiernan
